be.docarch.odt2braille.addon
Class SettingsDialog

java.lang.Object
  be.docarch.odt2braille.addon.SettingsDialog

public class SettingsDialog
extends java.lang.Object

Show an OpenOffice.org dialog window for adjusting the braille settings. The dialog has 10 tabs:

  • General Settings
  • Language Settings
  • Typeface Settings
  • Paragraph Settings
  • Heading Settings
  • List Settings
  • Table Settings
  • Pagenumber Settings
  • Table of Contents Settings
  • Special Symbols Settings
  • Mathematics Settings
